text: Ross Russell (born 18 December 1967) is a Trinidadian retired footballer who played for Defence Force and the national team as a goalkeeper. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Trinidad and Tobago footballers Category:Trinidad and Tobago international footballers Category:Defence Force F.C. players Category:TT Pro League players Category:Association football goalkeepers
